SERVICE DESK BEST PRACTICES:

1. Verify User Identity
   - Never reset without verification
   - Ask security questions
   - Check ID if in-person

2. Document Everything
   - Record all actions
   - Note troubleshooting steps
   - Log time to resolution

3. Communicate Clearly
   - Explain issue to user
   - Provide simple steps
   - Follow up after resolution

4. Escalate When Needed
   - If issue persists, escalate
   - Document for higher support
   - Don't spend >15 mins on one ticket

5. Know Your Tools
   - Microsoft 365 Admin
   - Entra ID
   - Exchange Admin
   - Teams Admin
   - Each has specific purpose

